"Dr. Margarite Griesz-Brisson MD, PhD is a Consultant Neurologist and Neurophysiologist with a PhD in Pharmacology, with special interest in neurotoxicology, environmental medicine, neuroregeneration and neuroplasticity. This is what she has to say about masks and their effects on our brains:

“The re-breathing of our exhaled air will without a doubt create oxygen deficiency and a flooding of carbon dioxide. We know the human brain is very sensitive to oxygen deprivation. There are nerve cells for example in the hippocampus, that can’t be longer than 3 minutes without oxygen – they cannot survive.

The acute warning symptoms are headaches, drowsiness, dizziness, issues in concentration, slowing down of the reaction time – reactions of the cognitive system.
However, when you have chronic oxygen deprivation, all of those symptoms disappear, because you get used to it. But your efficiency will remain impaired and the under supply of oxygen in your brain continues to progress.

We know that neuro-degenerative diseases take years to decades to develop. If today you forget your phone number, the breakdown in your brain would have already started 20 or 30 years ago.

While you’re thinking you’ve gotten used to wearing your mask and re-breathing your own exhaled air, the degenerative processes in your brain are getting amplified as your oxygen deprivation continues.

The second problem is that nerve cells in your brain are unable to divide themselves normally. So in case our governments will generously allow us to get rid of the masks and go back to breathing oxygen freely again in a few months, the lost nerve cells will no longer be regenerated. What is gone is gone.

— — — I do not wear a mask, I need my brain to think. I want to have a clear head when I deal with my patients, and not be in a carbon dioxide induced anaesthesia.

— — — There is no unfounded medical exemption from face masks because oxygen deprivation is dangerous for every single brain. It must be the free decision of every human being whether they want to wear a mask that is absolutely ineffective to protect themselves from a virus.

For children and adolescents, masks are an absolute no-no. Children and adolescents have an extremely active and adaptive immune system and they need a constant interaction with the microbiome of the Earth. Their brain is also incredibly active, as it is has so much to learn. The child’s brain, or the youth’s brain is thirsting for oxygen. The more metabolically active the organ is, the more oxygen it requires. In children and adolescents every organ is metabolically active.

To deprive a child’s or an adolescent’s brain from oxygen, or to restrict it in any way, is not only dangerous to their health, it is absolutely criminal. Oxygen deficiency inhibits the development of the brain, and the damage that has taken place as a result CANNOT be reversed.

The child needs the brain to learn, and the brain needs oxygen to function. We don’t need a clinical study for that. This is simple, indisputable physiology. Conscious and purposely induced oxygen deficiency is an absolutely deliberate health hazard, and an absolute medical contraindication.

An absolute medical contraindication in medicine means that this drug, this therapy, this method or measure should not be used – is not allowed to be used. To coerce an entire population to use an absolute medical contraindication by force, there must be definite and serious reasons for this, and the reasons must be presented to competent interdisciplinary and independent bodies to be verified and authorised.

When in ten years, dementia is going to increase exponentially, and the younger generations couldn’t reach their god-given potential, it won’t help to say “we didn’t need the masks”.

— — — How can a veterinarian, a software distributor, a business man, an electrical car manufacturer and a physicist decided on matters regarding the health of the entire population? Please dear colleagues, we all have to wake up.
I know how damaging oxygen deprivation is for the brain, cardiologist knows it for the heart, the pulmonologist knows it for the lungs. Oxygen deprivation damages every single organ.

Where are our health departments, our health insurance, our medical associations? It would have been their duty to be vehemently against the lock down and to stop it and stop it from the very beginning.

Why do the medical boards give punishments to doctors who give people exemptions? Does the person or the doctor seriously have to prove that oxygen deprivation harms people? What kind of medicine are our doctors and medical associations representing?

Who is responsible for this crime? The ones who want to enforce it? The ones who let it happen and play along, or the ones who don’t prevent it?

column31: NEW BRUNSWICK MANDATES MASKS, THOUGH INFLUENZA FAR WORSE At midnight October 9, 2020, the New Brunswick government made masks mandatory for all people aged 2 and up, except for those with a medical exemption. The move is a curious one considering the 2019-2020 influenza viruses (Influenza A and Influenza B) exacted a far greater toll on people in New Brunswick than did Covid-19, the much feared killer virus. There were 2,351 influenza cases and 268 hospitalizations and 11 deaths associated with influenza versus only 238 Covid-19 cases, 21 hospitalizations and only 2 deaths. (1)(2) The 2 deaths occurred in the same long-term care facility, Manoir de la Vallée. Both residents were between the ages of 80-89 with the last death taking place almost four-months ago on June 13, 2020. Even based on the small Covid-19 numbers alone, the mask mandate seems severe as New Brunswick seems to have contained the virus well. In a population of 781,476, only 0.029% of the population has tested positive and the 2 deaths account for 0.00026% of the population. Not exactly numbers of pandemic proportions...or even last year's flu. With such figures and a respiratory infection comparison in mind, is a mandatory mask order in New Brunswick justified? (1) N.B. flu report: https://www2.gnb.ca/content/gnb/en/corporate/promo/flu/SeasonalFluReport.html (2) N.B. Covid-19 report: https://experience.arcgis.com/experience/8eeb9a2052d641c996dba5de8f25a8aa ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- LE NOUVEAU-BRUNSWICK OBLIGE LE PORT DU MASQUE, MALGRÉ QUE L'INFLUENZA EST BIEN PIRE À minuit le 9 octobre 2020, le gouvernement du Nouveau-Brunswick a rendu les masques obligatoires pour toutes les personnes âgées de 2 ans et plus, à l'exception de celles bénéficiant d'une exemption médicale. Cette décision est curieuse étant donné que les virus de la grippe 2019-2020 (grippe A et grippe B) ont fait des ravages beaucoup plus importants au Nouveau-Brunswick que le Covid-19, le virus tueur tant redouté. Il y a eu 2 351 cas de grippe et 268 hospitalisations et 11 décès associés à la grippe contre seulement 238 cas de Covid-19, 21 hospitalisations et seulement 2 décès. (1) (2) Les 2 décès sont survenus dans le même établissement de soins de longue durée, le Manoir de la Vallée. Les deux résidents étaient âgés de 80 à 89 ans, le dernier décès ayant eu lieu il y a près de quatre mois, le 13 juin 2020. Même en se basant uniquement sur les petits chiffres du Covid-19, le port du masque obligatoire semble sévère car le Nouveau-Brunswick semble avoir bien contenu le virus. Sur une population de 781 476 habitants, seulement 0,029% de la population a été testée positive et les 2 décès représentent 0,00026% de la population. Pas exactement des nombres de proportions pandémiques ... ou même de la grippe de l'année dernière. Compte tenu de ces chiffres et d'une comparaison des infections respiratoires, une ordonnance de masque obligatoire au Nouveau-Brunswick est-elle justifiée? (1) N.B. rapport sur la grippe: https://www2.gnb.ca/content/gnb/en/corporate/promo/flu/SeasonalFluReport.html (2) N.B. Rapport Covid-19: https://experience.arcgis.com/experience/8eeb9a2052d641c996dba5de8f25a8aa

Oct8 by Jon Rappoport

The key phrase there is: “Since no quantified virus isolates of the 2019-nCoV are currently available…”

Every object that exists can be quantified, which is to say, measured. The use of the term “quantified” in that phrase means: the CDC has no measurable amount of the virus, because it is unavailable.

THE CDC HAS NO VIRUS.

A further tip-off is the use of the word ‘isolates.” This means NO ISOLATED VIRUS IS AVAILABLE.

Another way to put it: NO ONE HAS AN ISOLATED SPECIMEN OF THE COVID-19 VIRUS.
NO ONE HAS ISOLATED THE COVID-19 VIRUS.
THEREFORE, NO ONE HAS PROVED THAT IT EXISTS.

And using this test, the CDC and every other public health agency in the world are counting COVID cases and deaths…and governments have instituted lockdowns and economic devastation using those case and death numbers as justification.

column31: Tons of Cv19 propaganda has been generated by various factions of the globalist establishment and industry. Add to that the Western establishment’s worldwide censorship, and it’s infecting the public ability to think and reason concerning everything attached to Cv19. From the article as follows: This year has been the first test of lockdownism. It included the most intrusive, comprehensive, and near-global controls of human beings and their movements in recorded history. Even in countries where the rule of law and liberties are sources of national pride, people were put under house arrest. Their churches and businesses were closed. The police have been unleashed to enforce it all and arrest open dissent. The devastation compares with wartime except that it was a government-imposed war on people’s right to move and exchange freely. We still cannot travel. And remarkably, after all of this, what remains missing is the empirical evidence, from anywhere in the world, that this shocking and unprecedented regime had any effect on controlling much less stopping the virus. Even more remarkably, the few places that remained fully open (South Dakota, Sweden, Tanzania, Belarus), points out Will Jones, “lost no more than 0.06% of their population to the virus,” in contrast to high deaths lockdown New York and Britain. Early on, most people went along, thinking that it was somehow necessary and short term. Two weeks stretched to 30 days which stretched to 7 months, and now we are told there will never be a time when we don’t practice this new public-policy faith. It’s a new totalitarianism. And with all such regimes, there is one set of rules for the rulers and another for the ruled. The language apparatus is now incredibly familiar: curve flattening, spread slowing, social distancing, targeted layered containment, non-pharmaceutical intervention. The enemy is the virus and anyone who isn’t living their life solely to avoid contamination. Because you can’t see the virus, that usually means generating a paranoia of The Other: someone unlike you has the virus. Anyone could be a super spreader and you can recognize them by their noncompliance. If Robert Glass or Neil Ferguson deserve to be called the founders of this movement, one of its most famous practitioners is Anthony Fauci of the National Institutes for Health. His vision of the future is positively shocking: it includes restrictions on who you can have in your home, the end of all large events, the end of travel, perhaps an attack on pets, and the effective dismantlement of all cities.

column36:
Open and honest discussion and information sharing are the hallmarks of good faith bargaining, United Nurses of Alberta Labour Relations Director David Harrigan reminded his counterpart at Alberta Health Services in a letter seeking a meeting sent today. 

Unfortunately, Harrigan told AHS Executive Director of Negotiations and Labour Relations Leland McEwen, that has not been UNA’s experience with the province’s largest health care employer during the current round of negotiations.

Harrigan cited Finance Minister Travis Toews’s misleading claim UNA is “playing games in the media” by trying to resume bargaining for a new collective agreement, the constantly shifting and often contradictory stories by government and AHS officials about plans to lay off nurses, and the unwillingness of senior AHS officials to correct false statements made by the health minister.

Harrigan asked for a meeting with McEwen to clarify the overall impact on FTE of workforce changes to the direct nursing bargaining unit represented by UNA mentioned in a letter sent yesterday by McEwen to Harrigan. Statements in the letter were at variance with claims made by Health Minister Tyler Shandro during his Oct. 13 news conference.

Read the statement online: https://www.una.ca/1164/una-labour-relations-director-seeks-meeting-with-top-ahs-negotiations-official

column36:
WHY WE SHOULDN'T WEAR MASKS!

Wearing a mask on the long term is destroying your health. What is wiser? 99%of population putting their life in danger or 1% isolate and the rest are supporting and taking care of them? 

Dr. Margarite Griesz-Brisson MD, PhD is a Consultant Neurologist and Neurophysiologist with a PhD in Pharmacology, with special interest in neurotoxicology, environmental medicine, neuroregeneration and neuroplasticity. This is what she has to say about masks and their effects on our brains:

“The rebreathing of our exhaled air will without a doubt create oxygen deficiency and a flooding of carbon dioxide. We know that the human brain is very sensitive to oxygen depravation. There are nerve cells for example in the hippocampus, that can’t be longer than 3 minutes without oxygen - they cannot survive. 
The acute warning symptoms are headaches, drowsiness, dizziness, issues in concentration, slowing down of the reaction time - reactions of the cognitive system. 

However, when you have chronic oxygen depravation, all of those symptoms disappear, because you get used to it. But your efficiency will remain impaired and the undersupply of oxygen in your brain continues to progress.

We know that neurodegenerative diseases take years to decades to develop. If today you forget your phone number, the breakdown in your brain would have already started 20 or 30 years ago.

While you’re thinking, that you have gotten used to wearing your mask and rebreathing your own exhaled air, the degenerative processes in your brain are getting amplified as your oxygen deprivation continues.

The second problem is that the nerve cells in your brain are unable to divide themselves normally. So in case our governments will generously allow as to get rid of the masks and go back to breathing oxygen freely again in a few months, the lost nerve cells will no longer be regenerated. What is gone is gone.

— — — I do not wear a mask, I need my brain to think. I want to have a clear head when I deal with my patients, and not be in a carbon dioxide induced anaesthesia. 

— — —  There is no unfounded medical exemption from face masks because oxygen deprivation is dangerous for every single brain. It must be the free decision of every human being whether they want to wear a mask that is absolutely ineffective to protect themselves from a virus. 

For children and adolescents, masks are an absolute no-no. Children and adolescents have an extremely active and adaptive immune system and they need a constant interaction with the microbiome of the Earth. Their brain is also incredibly active, as it is has so much to learn. The child’s brain, or the youth’s brain is thirsting for oxygen. The more metabolically active the organ is, the more oxygen it requires.  In children and adolescents every organ is metabolically active.

To deprive a child’s or an adolescent’s brain from oxygen, or to restrict it in any way, is not only dangerous to their health, it is absolutely criminal. Oxygen deficiency inhibits the development of the brain, and the damage that has taken place as a result CANNOT be reversed. 

The child needs the brain to learn, and the brain needs oxygen to function.  We don’t need a clinical study for that. This is simple, indisputable physiology. Conscious and purposely induced oxygen deficiency is an absolutely deliberate health hazard, and an absolute medical contraindication. 

An absolute medical contraindication in medicine means that this drug, this therapy, this method or measure should not be used - is not allowed to be used. To coerce an entire population to use an absolute medical contraindication by force, there must be definite and serious reasons for this, and the reasons must be presented to competent interdisciplinary and independent bodies to be verified and authorised. 

When in ten years, dementia is going to increase exponentially, and the younger generations couldn’t reach their god-given potential, it won’t help to say “we didn’t need the masks”.

— — — How can a veterinarian, a software distributer, a business man, an electrical car manufacturer and a physicist decided on matters regarding the health of the entire population? Please dear colleagues, we all have to wake up.

I know how damaging oxygen depravation is for the brain, cardiologist knows it for the heart, the pulmonologist knows it for the lungs. Oxygen deprivation damages every single organ. 

Where are our health departments, our health insurance, our medical associations? It would have been their duty to be vehemently against the lockdown and to stop it and stop it from the very beginning. 

Why do the medical boards give punishments to doctors who give people exemptions? Does the person or the doctor seriously have to prove that oxygen depravation harms people? What kind of medicine are our doctors and medical associations representing?

Who is responsible for this crime? The ones (truncated)

column34: M 0 ALL ALL The Telegraph LOCKDOWNS LOCKDOWN URE MUST NOT TELEGRAPH.CO.UK Herd immunity could have saved more lives than lockdown, study suggests
column36:
HERD IMMUNITY COULD HAVE SAVED MORE LIVES THAN LOCKDOWNS: EDINBURGH UNIVERSITY STUDY

"Blanket social distancing and the closure of schools may have cost more lives than if herd immunity had been allowed to build slowly in the community, a University of Edinburgh study found.

A reanalysis of the Imperial College modelling that led to lockdown in March shows that shutting schools and preventing youngsters from mingling may have had the counterintuitive effect of actually killing more people.

In a study published in the British Medical Journal, Edinburgh University predicted that over the entire course of the pandemic, keeping children out of classrooms would increase deaths by between 80,000 and 95,000. Likewise, social distancing of everyone, rather than just the over-70s, could cost between 149,000 and 178,000 lives. Experts say the virus was able to spread faster to vulnerable people once lockdown measures were introduced than if some level of immunity had been allowed to build up in the young. 

It comes as thousands of scientists across the world signed the Great Barrington Declaration, calling for an end to lockdown for young and healthy people.

The Government locked down the country after Imperial modelling showed that 500,000 people could die and the NHS would be overwhelmed. But Imperial had also predicted that no mitigation strategy could lower deaths to fewer than 200,000 without a vaccine, and suppressing the virus would merely delay an even deadlier resurgence.

The authors of the new paper, who rediscovered the figures in their reappraisal, said the Government appeared to have chosen to protect the NHS in the short term, rather than save lives throughout the whole epidemic. Although it reduced peak demand for ICU beds, it prolonged the epidemic, resulting in more Covid-19 deaths in long-term.

Lead author Graeme Ackland, Professor of computer simulation at the University of Edinburgh, said: 'In March the Government had to make a decision: did they want to save lives or beds? Lockdown does mean that the number of deaths goes down, so there is a short-term gain, but it leads to long-term pain. If you had done nothing, it would all be over by now. It wouldn’t even have been completely lunatic to do nothing.'

The study also found that shutting schools ‘leads to more overall deaths from Covid-19’ than allowing them to remain open. 'This is because it prevents herd immunity building up among the healthy and young, who face only a tiny risk of dying from the disease. The virus would bounce back as soon as measures involving school closures are lifted, infecting more vulnerable populations and resulting in ‘more deaths, but later’. Figures showing the dangers of closing schools and blanket social distancing were reported in the original Imperial paper, but many experts did not notice them, it is claimed. 'I talked to people on SPI-M and Sage and they hadn’t seen them,' added Professoor Ackland.

‘Lockdowns essentially just postpone these deaths and prevent immunity building up... in some cases resulting in more deaths long-term. The way out of any epidemic is herd immunity, which is when enough people in the population are infected that the virus can’t spread. We need to focus on protecting older people who are going to be affected by coronavirus, not people who are not,' stated Professor Ackland."

A vote by mail ballot collected by a ballot harvester does NOT have to include the name or signature of the harvester on the identification envelope in order to be valid.

A ballot harvester is NOT required to document the vote by mail ballots chain of custody in any way.

A ballot harvester is NOT required to disclose to a voter who they are working on behalf of or if they are being paid to collect ballots.

A ballot harvester is NOT required to provide any kind of documentation/receipt when collecting a vote by mail ballot.

Election officials are NOT required to obtain any identifying information, including names, of ballot harvesters when they return collected ballots.

Election officials are NOT required to maintain a list of persons who collect and submit collected ballots, regardless of how many ballots they submit.

ANY individual is eligible to harvest ballots, including:

Non-California residents
Illegal immigrants
Foreign nationals
ANY entity may have and compensate its employees to harvest ballots (so long as the compensation is not on a per ballot basis), including:

Campaigns
Non-profit organizations
Businesses, including corporations
Labor unions
Churches
Ballot harvesters may collect an unlimited number of ballots.
Campaigns may pay third party vendors to harvest ballots (so long as the compensation is not on a per ballot basis).

Election officials are not required to categorize harvested ballots or otherwise distinguish them from vote by mail ballots submitted by other means.

column36:
"Borrowed" from elsewhere on Facebook:

What is the normal process for a "reportable disease" (disease of concern to public health) outbreak/epidemic?
1. "Cases" are symptomatic patients - and often those requiring medical attention.
1. One of the most important epidemiological tools for tracking the impact that a disease has on the population is "prevalence".  This is essentially the percentage of "cases" in the population at or over a given time period.
1. "Cases" are reported for the date the symptoms started OR the date that the diagnostic test was performed.
1. The number of "cases", "hospitalizations" and "deaths" attributed to the disease can be adjusted down retrospectively if it is discovered that the case did not actually qualify (i.e. was not the disease) - AND the numbers and epidemiological curve for the ORIGINAL time period would be adjusted.

What is currently happening in Ontario (and probably wherever you live):
1. They have moved the goalposts on this one.  The case definition for COVID-19 (SARS-CoV-2) includes individuals who do NOT have ANY symptoms at the time of testing, nor develop them during the entire typical incubation time period (i.e. 10-14 days max.).

The majority of people being tested in Ontario at this time - do NOT have ANY symptoms (i.e. are asymptomatic) and are being tested voluntarily.
1. The Government of Ontario and public health departments KNOWINGLY AND WILLINGLY reports raw data numbers (i.e. new "cases") without the context of the number of people being tested (the "population" or sample size).  Raw data numbers without context are not only deceptive and confusing to the general public - but are nothing but a tool to stoke fear.

(Sidebar example:  The number of sexual assaults in New York City's Central Park tend to go up when ice cream sales in the park increase.  Those two raw data numbers - without the context of the warm weather - are deceptive.)

The day-to-day and rolling 7-day average prevalence  of COVID-19 from early June to today has essentially been at or below 1.2%.  ([https://covid-19.ontario.ca/data](https://covid-19.ontario.ca/data?fbclid=IwAR0aFxHnxvNzY0BA08lzk-P0dD7RfLAUAXDHBwYf-uPBTISe9_H4sx_MvvY) )

There has been NO 2nd wave during this period.  Barely a ripple.

There has been a massive increase in testing over that time period - and if one examines the number of "cases" in that context, they are not near as impressive or concerning.

The epidemic was essentially over at the end of May to beginning of June.

Since then we have simply had a [#casedemic](https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/casedemic?__eep__=6&__cft__%5B0%5D=AZXfP6u5oDpddkHpvmi40MTlkz4TqUEWNZxfaOu-ZKvSWkO9u2AY4T5JgROAON8pSb_-1h4BV9gZAzghotBNncuTJCOH0ESqWEVvVhhGHp6klyCuZRlN_xSVkGv679BNtut6zPiLetPM-FcxZnnVFFhRYeiRNxVHLnINpLo9wOkBpiIxxigiBYyyq2u2DbS3J1E&__tn__=%2ANK-R).
1. The Government of Ontario is KNOWLINGLY adding new "cases" to the daily numbers on the day the results are received/reported - not the day of the test.

This is concerning for 2 reasons:

a)  just a couple of days ago there was an over 90,000 test backlog for processing, and...

b)  they are now KNOWINGLY adding historic "cases", "hospitalizations" and "deaths" from March to the new daily numbers - thus falsely inflating those number and changing the epidemiological curve.
1. As the never-before-in-history case definition has falsely inflated the daily numbers (see the next section for more details) - will they retrospectively review all "cases" and remove those that showed no evidence of active infection (i.e. symptomatic)?  As the case definition also affects what is reported for "hospitalizations" and "deaths" - will those numbers be audited and changed accordingly as well?

A Quick Word About the Tests:

There has been a lot of talk about a "false positive" rate of 50%.

Actually, the false positive rate is significantly more than 50% (over 90%) if the prevalence is around 1% (which is where is has been in Ontario for almost 4 months).

See the narrative before and after the 3rd table in this article:

[https://globalnews.ca/.../what-do-false-positive-covid.../](https://globalnews.ca/news/7323725/what-do-false-positive-covid-19-tests-mean/?fbclid=IwAR2nJnqGfH6utgI0WFtnbyGNy0vYf3X2oitvrD66qxuE4WvIS_J4K9bCmDY)

The PPV is interpreted as the probability that someone that has tested positive actually has the disease.

When the disease has low prevalence, the PPV of the test can be very low.

We know that there will be a significantly higher false positive rate if a significant number of the test subjects are asymptomatic - partially due to an inherently lower prevalence, and partially due to the fact that the RT- PCR does not differentiate between dead virus particles from a past/historic exposure/infection and a current (truncated)

column31: The PlayBook: Legault-style — Cashhh your Check! (BEWARE: Government of Quebec strategy: a case study for other governments!) * We want to vaccinate everyone (because we have made a good package deal that advances our interests!!!) but we will not tell them, we will tell them that it is for their own good and the one and only way to put an end to these “emergency health measures” (that we created) Furthermore, any other solution will be discarded, even if it works and they will be told that it is not scientific. *We will do PCR tests (even if the PCR tests are not reliable, not recommended for diagnosis by the test creator himself, do not test for the virus COVID, and have a very high rate of positives (even if they are are false positives). This will give us the power to say that there are a lot of cases and that it is a very great risk for the population. *We are going to scare the population. The media will have a fear-mongering discourse,, with only one admitted ideology, “Ours”, and we will ridicule all those who see through the cracks of our project and criticize it. *We will get everyone to wear masks until the vaccines are ready ... to keep people in a state of fear and start to assert our agenda into their intimate spaces and see who obeys our guidelines and who does not. *We will wreak havoc between those who adopt the mask and those who will not want to put it on (because they have read scientific studies on cotton masks and the like, have listened to epidemiologists, and we have read about the highly detailed protocols by surgeons and the like, nothing to do with mass usage, and because it blocks breathing and free expression. And can contribute to bacterial infections. And because it keeps the population in a Chernobyl-like ambiance.) But as Niccolò Machiavelli said: “Divide and conquer”, “Dividere e conquistare” is a winner tactic. *We will make sure that the "stars-system" in Quebec laugh at people who see the flaws in our strategy. They give them names and label them with insults and call them “conspiracy theorists" so that people are afraid of them and are not heard, and to avoid real debate by saying that '"They are dangerous." This is called "gaslighting": saying that people are crazy when they really have figured it out. We will discredit there people, and any spokesperson who thinks critically about the situation. We will even gag professionals via their professional order and threaten them to lose their right to practice. Thus, we have the monopoly of the narrative. (A great place to be!) *Our bureaucrats have consulted studies on human psychology to confirm the tactics of psychological control (mind-control) via marketing so that the population follows without questioning and even puts pressure on others to become little “balcony” soldiers and “social media warriors" to continue our work, a successful strategy that is easily achieved by igniting fear with all the false positives discovered with the PCR tests. Use tactics that touch on fear of ostracization, fear of being different, and of being exposed: tactics used in all dictatorships. Above all, don't allow freedom of expression and debate. (Well detailed in this Yale University study: [https://clinicaltrials.gov/ct2/show/NCT04460703](https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fclinicaltrials.gov%2Fct2%2Fshow%2FNCT04460703%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR20wfPCXd1azQ8zgR85Ediqb6GLuL2N1HXgE69dp3im44eMZzvbai5Fcdk&h=AT1qDQm4NdbB8ZXaqV9W4M9Ii-mpzzL7gyKRNoBlh_zD95Bi4c1yVFv-6U0OLd_LMjf_7vQ0F0G5ONPhQT7KY3fA6m7qZ80_AGIvhXtst91wFF9NBCUKASghrdLmqT8MIlj87k7i7hz7r6mtjU7ZzVg&__tn__=-UK-R&c[0]=AT38d88207BXpasChxoMEiLJ7afxTuAwBbj0zIdlKTs2j7vms_r3b-8za_9kXIS7y9ocJa743rxj01t2Stiy1JU7RTXVap9ICYzW3OmhQqoNsLA02J1UCIZCHJX8lV97LlYQsjQPG_W9-fkoM_P-2w)) *People who see through the cracks will start to protest, and rally in demonstrations. *We will increase the ineffective PCR tests to show that the COVIDs cases are increasing. Because more tests give more positives (even if people aren't sick with COVID). *The media will panic. *We will blame the people who use the right to freedom of expression to speak out against the nonsense. Great way to get them to shut up. *The population that is sensitive to mind control tactics, subliminal suggestions, otherwise known as “suggestology”, will start to panic and continue the work started by the media by accusing the people who have identified the government's manipulations. *We are going to take away even more rights, such as the right to see friends, to get together, not to wear a mask, all essential needs for a social species, we will close businesses, restaurants, bars, to ignite rage in the population and we will direct their rage at the scapegoats identified with tags to cover up our game and scam. (And during this time, pass law 66 to usurp even more power). We will use the emotional charge of a traumatized population to attack critical people who see the government's real (truncated)

2015 in California, thousands of us rose to fight CA SB277 and protect our children and health freedom against big industry & global agendas.

column31: Let Your Children Be - Let Your Children Breathe>>> [https://www.facebook.com/paul.turner.39589149/posts/10218686612384150](https://www.facebook.com/paul.turner.39589149/posts/10218686612384150?__cft__[0]=AZUPrYEdxaNMeNfda-L4f2uCyRVM5Eb3T8Y8Qa0cLUgg3DRsmMzphZUaCjfXo9rBclf1Thl8o4vlfpldVZM32e4AI1WFWN7_mgXyFepLBPsmxDmrnVD_S1qY0CWhmbS_ERE&__tn__=-UK-R) -------------------------- Today on the playground my two boys and their best friend ran and jumped and climbed and laughed in the warm October sun with a fall breeze in the air. -------------------- On the sidelines stood a boy about the age of my older son and his friend, watching them with his eyes peering out above a blue checkered mask. His dad stood next to him, wearing his own black mask, and I saw him prodding his son to go play, to go run and jump with our three boys. -------------------- Eventually, after some pushing, the boy shyly approached the others and seemed to be trying hard to figure out how to interact with them. He ran alongside them and after them but didn't run with them. He stood next to the slide as they tumbled happily down but didn't try it himself. I couldn't tell what he was thinking because his masked face had no visible expression and I didn't hear his voice, not even once. He didn't try to speak, not even an attempt from behind the mask. I tried encouraging my four year old to make an effort with the boy, but he had little interest in a playmate he couldn't see or talk to. -------------------- After some time I noticed the boy would try reaching out for their hands or would motion for them to come follow him, but still no voice. No sounds from him. Like a small mime.. he played charades any time he had something to tell the others. He seemed to me like a silent shadow and stood in sad contrast to the loud happy chaos of our boys all around him. I began to wonder if it wasn't the mask at all as I had thought but maybe a developmental delay or perhaps he was deaf or couldn't speak. -------------------- After what felt like a long time- it seemed his dad must have come to the realization that none of us were wearing masks, so maybe it would be alright for a few moments to let his son breathe in the fresh outdoor air and to run around exerting himself with the full capacity to inhale. -------------------- Almost at once, when that blue checkered mask was removed, this boy came to life. His voice rose up out of nowhere and his personality sprung to life and he began playing and laughing and being a normal four year old boy and the four boys began to chase each other and hide in corners laughing at their own private jokes. -------------------- I felt relief for him. His father had set him free. -------------------- I have never once put a mask on my children, and no matter how many times I have to see it, it still breaks my heart and fills me with fury when I see a child in a mask. -------------------- Children need to be heard. They need to know that their voices are valuable and that their words are meaningful and that they do not deserve to spend their lives with their individual, God given faces hidden away. They need attention, non stop exhausting attention, and as I was reminded today, these masks are a barrier that do not allow them to feel that they are worthy of being paid any attention to. Take away someone's identity as they are still trying to figure out their identity and watch how easily you've crippled them. -------------------- This boy on the playground with his mask on had given up. Instead of raising his voice he had been silenced. Instead of feeling like he was worthy of friends he watched life happen from the outside. At the age of four he was already learning that trying to be heard over a piece of cloth was nearly impossible and no one probably cared what he had to say anyway, because with a mask on his face he wasn't Joey (*name changed), he was just another faceless mask in the herd. I felt his freedom the moment that mask was removed. I felt the weight lifted away from him. -------------------- I don't care who reads this and walks away or blocks me, I don't care, because I am done. So here it is. If you have a mask on your child you are failing them as a parent. You are not keeping them safe or keeping anyone else safe. You are smothering them, putting a literal muzzle over their face and stifling all the thoughts and dreams they should be expressing and that they need the world to know about. You are crushing their independence and all the traits that make them, them. You are preventing free thought and producing yet another cog in the wheel of conformity which is the very last thing this world needs right now. -------------------- You won't ever find my children in a mask. You'll find them on the playground being normal children, confident in knowing that their voices will never be stifled and that they have value beyond being a human shield. They will know what it is to make eye contact and for (truncated)

column31: PETITION TO SIGN AND SHARE: Our Student Kids are not Convicts: "Young people across the UK are being locked down, isolated, and betrayed. Promised and paying for a normal university education and experience, many are receiving something that looks very different: limited or no face-to-face teaching, limited extra-curricular and social experiences, solitary isolation in sterile accommodation. Many are living away from parents for the first time and are either entirely alone, or holed up with people they’ve only just met. Patrolled by security guards and police dogs many are suffering from limited access to food, washing facilities, and most of all, human contact. This is an inhumane and disproportionate infringement of their human rights. Many are already struggling with their mental health. For this privilege, they are paying around £15,000 for tuition and accommodation. Some in the media have blamed students for spreading Covid-19, but students are in fact being subjected to harsher restrictions than almost everybody else. We appreciate that universities are operating under severe constraints, and that many are doing their very best to give students the highest quality teaching and a university experience that is as 'normal' as possible. However, the unfortunate reality is severe issues remain for large numbers of students. Many campuses have become ghost towns, with food and drink outlets shut down. Some university dining halls do not allow even six people to sit together, providing instead single tables in exam-hall format, or pushing sandwiches through bedroom doors. Food deliveries are restricted. Sport and exercise is often non-existent. Meanwhile the population at large continues to eat in restaurants, frequent bars and pubs and work-out in the gym. These are our children. We are betraying them when they need us most. And we betray ourselves too, since this generation are the best hope we have of clawing ourselves back up from the depths of the economic abyss we’re about to find ourselves in. Extensive empirical evidence makes it clear that young people are not at serious risk from Covid 19. Nor are they to blame for it. They have lost the most and gained the least from the measures enforced to tackle it and if we do not act soon their life chances may be damaged beyond repair. They deserve a proper university education and quality of life. We call upon the Higher Education sector to to immediately institute a Minimum University Provision. This should at a minimum include: Restoration of in-person learning for tutorials and seminars. Whilst we understand that - for now - large gatherings cannot take place, the same concern should not apply to tutorials and seminars which could be arranged in small groups or in bubbles. Restoration of extra-curricular activities and societies. These are crucial to social interaction and to mental and physical health and are the bedrock of the university experience. Online substitutes do not meet these needs. Restoration of opportunities for social interaction in line with government advice. Every dining hall to at a minimum allow tables of up to six; food outlets and bars to be open in accordance with the law. Targeted and specific quarantines only. The sweeping lockdown of entire halls of residence is neither logical nor sustainable. Instead, isolate only where kitchen or washing facilities are shared. This may be per room, per flat, or per floor. Whole buildings must not be quarantined. Pastoral care for young people who are isolating. These students are barely out of childhood and many are struggling with very little support. When isolating, they need help with food, washing, and other practical arrangements. They also need welfare provision including contact with mental health practitioners where needed. If this minimum provision cannot be met, then students must be allowed to leave and universities must provide full online learning for no more than two thirds of the tuition fee (as per correspondence learning at The Open University). All accommodation costs should be refunded to those who wish to return home."

HOW ACCURATE IS THE COVID-19 DATA THAT GUIDES LOCKDOWN MEASURES?

With a purported second wave now under way, lockdown measures have again intensified across Canada. The data used to drive the emergency health policies, however, do not stand on solid, credible ground.

Deaths, for the first time in history, are not being attributed to an actual cause of death but an accompanying infection, as is the case with Covid-19. This new guideline was recommended by the World Health Organization (WHO), but the public was never given an explanation for this change in coding deaths by the WHO or its governments. 

On June 23, 2020, Ontario Minister of Health Christine Elliott confirmed that "there are situations where there are other pre-existing conditions that may actually be the cause of the loss, rather than Covid. Covid is there but may not have been the cause of death." (1)

Curiously, Canadian media outlets have not reported or questioned this epidemiologically significant change in the way that deaths are recorded.

The reporting of daily new cases has been the one metric that has remained since the start of the WHO-called Covid-19 pandemic. The initial projection of deaths, the metric by which many countries instituted lockdown measures, quickly fell from government and media narrative, as those numbers were grossly exaggerated worldwide. In Canada, 226,000 to 526,000 deaths (est. 2% fatality) were initially projected under strong measures. 

Since then, PCR tests have been the global tool that governments have used to drive emergency policies and measures. The accuracy of reporting positive Covid-19 cases has recently come under scrutiny, however, especially since a New York Times review of positive cases in three states revealed that as many as 90% of cases had "barely any virus" and were likely not infectious. (3)

The reason: PCR tests were set at levels that magnified the amount of virus 100x - 1000x the actual amount in the body. 

Earlier on July 30, 2020, Ontario’s associate chief medical officer of health, Dr. Barbara Yaffe validated this finding by the New York Times review, “If you’re testing in a population that doesn’t have very much Covid, you’ll get false positives almost half the time. That is, the person doesn’t actually have Covid.”

With such inaccuracies in the reporting of new cases during a purported second wave of Covid-19, should the government abandon this metric to gauge the severity of Covid-19 and its potential impact on Canadians and instead use the number of hospitalizations and deaths--numbers less subject to gross inaccuracies--to guide our health measures? 

With the health and financial destinies of millions of Canadians resting in the hands of accurate and transparent government data and policies, it's a move that makes medical and political sense. 

(1) https://www.680news.com/2020/06/23/toronto-child-under-9-dies-with-covid-19-but-not-as-a-result-of-the-virus/ 

(2) https://www.ctvnews.ca/health/coronavirus/pm-trudeau-this-will-be-the-new-normal-until-a-vaccine-is-developed-1.4889651

(3) https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/29/health/coronavirus-testing.html

QUELLE EST LA PRÉCISION DES DONNÉES COVID-19 QUI GUIDENT LES MESURES SANITAIRES?

Alors que la prétendue deuxième vague est en cours, les mesures sanitaires se sont de nouveau intensifiées partout au Canada. Cependant, les données utilisées pour conduire les politiques sanitaires d'urgence ne reposent pas sur des bases solides et crédibles.

Les décès, pour la première fois dans l'histoire, ne sont pas attribués à une cause réelle de décès mais à une infection qui l'accompagne, comme c'est le cas avec Covid-19. Cette nouvelle directive a été recommandée par l'Organisation mondiale de la santé (OMS), mais le public n'a jamais reçu d'explication pour ce changement de codage des décès par l'OMS ou ses gouvernements.

Le 23 juin 2020, la ministre de la Santé de l'Ontario, Christine Elliott, a confirmé qu '"il y a des situations où il existe d'autres conditions préexistantes qui pourraient en fait être la cause de la perte, plutôt que Covid. Covid est là mais peut-être pas en avoir été la cause de la mort." (1)

Curieusement, les médias canadiens n'ont pas rapporté ni remis en question ce changement épidémiologiquement significatif dans la façon dont les décès sont enregistrés.

La publication des nouveaux cas quotidiens est la seule mesure qui est restée depuis le début de la pandémie du Covid-19, telle que nommée par l'OMS. La projection initiale des décès, la mesure par laquelle de nombreux pays ont institué des mesures de confinement, est rapidement tombée du récit du gouvernement et des médias, car ces chiffres étaient largement exagérés dans le monde. Worth and to our state.

Perhaps what is even more disappointing is the cultural loss this brings for ALL Texans.  The Fort Worth Stock Show is the largest of its kind.  It's not only a Texas tradition, it keeps Texas traditions alive.  

Stock Show President and General Manager, Brad Barnes announced the decision today, saying that the only other time the show was cancelled was at the height of World War II.  He stated, "Today we're in another war with an enemy that's invisible and quite deadly.  We feel a responsibility to be proactive, in order that COVID-19 is brought under control sooner rather than later. For fans of Fort Worth's oldest and largest public event, our common goal is to help bring the pandemic to an end so future Stock Shows won't be in jeopardy." 

The decision was made by their board, but on the advice of the Fort Worth Public Health Tecnocrats who advised.  People like Tarrant County Public Health Director Vinny Tanjea who is quoted by the local CBS affiliate, stating, “The health and safety of our community is of the utmost importance.  We support the Stock Show’s executive committee in making this difficult decision.”

Public Health TECHNOCRATS are the ones pushing this new normal of public health tyranny.  Barnes tells us we are fighting an invisible and deadly enemy.  Well, we would like a FACT check on that because that sounds a little like science fiction.

In fact, Indiana University just published a recent study that looks at its state's mortality rate by age.  Public Enemy number one for the public health TECHNOCRATS has a death rate of 0.26% for all age groups.  For people aged 12-40, the death rate is 0.01%.  And, for those between the age of 40-59, it is 0.12%.  

Do those numbers sound like a viral boogeyman to you?  to put it in perspective, small pox had a death rate of 30%.  Ebola has a death rate between 25-80%.  Those numbers are to be feared.  

A death rate of 0.26% is not something we should fear; it's not something we should give up liberty for; and it's not something to lose our culture over.

This is Texas--not California!  We better get it together or this new normal of public health tyranny will destroy our way of life. 

Let's do something about it.

column31: My weekly update of the coronavirus situation in Hamilton. Hamilton has a population of 536,917 people. As of Oct 9, 109,255 tests have been completed at Assessment Centres or other facilities (long term care homes, retirement homes, other congregate settings) with 8,174 new tests in the previous 7 days. There have been 1,296 confirmed and probable cases*. Of those cases, 531 cases (41%)** had underlying health issues (diabetes, cancer, heart/renal/chronic lung disease). Only 155 cases (12%) required hospitalization, with 2 hospitalizations in the previous 7 days. 1,120 people have recovered, with 92 recoveries in the previous 7 days. There are currently 127 active cases - 1 person out of every 4,227 people living in Hamilton. There have been 47 deaths***, an average of 7.83 per month since the first death on March 24, with 1 death in the previous 7 days (there has been only 2 deaths since the week ending Jul 31). The City doesnt list which deaths also had the aforementioned underlying health issues - all 47 could have come from the cases who had other health issues, but without specifics, it's reasonable to assume that of those 47 deaths, 18 (41%) had diabetes, cancer, or heart/renal/lung disease. All deaths were over 40 years old: 1 death between the ages of 40-49; 7 deaths between the ages of 60-69; 5 deaths between the ages of 70-79; 26 deaths between the ages of 80-89; 7 deaths between the ages of 90-99; and 1 death aged 100 or above. There have been no deaths under the age of 40, even though, presumably, 41% of the cases under 40 years of age had one of the underlying health conditions. The average age of the deceased is 81.32 years old - the life expectancy in Canada is 82.52 years old. Hamilton's mandatory mask bylaw came into effect on Jul 20. With the virus having a 14 day incubation period, Aug 3 was the first day where any impact of the mask bylaw would be evident. There have been 119 new cases in the last 7 days (the week-over-week running 10-day total fell from 22 on Jul 17, to 15 on Jul 31 - a 31.81% drop - without mandatory masks). 98.82% of all the tests completed were negative (of the people tested, only 1.18% tested positive****), resulting in only 0.24% of the population of Hamilton ever having been infected. Only 1.45% of new tests in the previous 7 days have been positive - 98.55% of those tests have been negative. Summarized statistics for the past 7 days: 8,174 tests, 119 cases, 92 recoveries, 2 hospitalizations, 1 death This is all publicly available, and independently verifiable information. It seems the use of mandatory masks in indoor spaces, including shops and public transport, has not prevented a second wave, and a global trend is being confirmed by Italy's epidemiological data: second wave spikes are only occurring in case numbers, not hospitalizations or deaths.

column36: In this time of social engineered crisis, who would you turn to for medical support and exemptions?   You would think your own physician --right?   This morning I ( Matthew Cameron) called my allopathic doctor to see how enlightened he was and what role he was playing in the pandemic here in Glengarry-Prescott-Russell.  After hearing his response to me I believe that he works along side the  medical cartel at the  Glengarry Memorial Hospital in Alexandria, Ontario, Canada and is part of the biggest fraudulent scheme perpetrated on Canadians . Lawyer Rocco Galati who is suing our government  on this very issue talks about this fraudulent scheme. You might say, why such words to describe their life saving work they do every day?  Let me explain…  When I asked for a mask exemption from this physician (who is about to retire anyways), he replied that he was only able to hand them out to a specific group of people, ‘the handicap’ who could not remove the mask.  I told him that physicians were able to help to hand medical exemptions in many cases for asthma or lack of oxygen causing anxiety attacks in some cases.  He responded that masks do not pose lack of oxygen and that there was a  study proving you can run a marathon and have no drop in levels of oxygen whatsoever.  He said you can find these on the internet and go look for them.  I then asked him for who funded the studies and who paid to do the study, and of course he didn’t know and didn’t seem to want to know neither.  I mentioned that industry science and independent science have different outcome  results  because of the industry having influence on the science.    Twice he told me in this short 5-minute conversation,  to find myself a new doctor that will exempt me from wearing a mask.  He also pointed out to stay home instead of wearing a mask and not to go out  in public.  Can you believe that?  He said it in a calm psychopathic voice too.  Like I was a threat to humanity.  I also mentioned to him that  we never had to wear masks for influenza, H1N1 or  Tuberculosis and we are under medical dictatorship.  He callously replied that we were wasting time and told me to have a nice day.   To which I replied same to you, have a nice day.  That’s it! Clearly, as I analyzed the situation and our conversation, I noticed that he was following orders from the World Health Organization and the Ontario Public Health.   He never asked once  how I was with that anxiety when I told him about my state of mind, just dismissed it saying its all psychological (in my head) about the anxiety and that my oxygen was fine (over the phone).  I also questioned his lack of patient care by dismissing all of my concerns as he tried once again to rule over my body and my choices.  I  can only imagine how devasting this kind of reaction would have been for those that are  facing depression, anxiety, or who are simply alone or without any moral support.  What would they have done or how could they react to such words from a doctor who has no empathy?  Could such words from a physician in Ontario cause more anxiety and depression leading to suicide increase rates throughout our society in the name of profit, control and financial gains for the pharmaceutical industry?   Are they pushing our younger generations to become the next generation of slaves for the medical industry?  Could their type of response and orders that were given to them by their medical boards be inflicting more emotional pain and discomfort to simply push more of their toxic psychobabble onto the people leading them to accept the masks and also comply to the vaccine agendas?  When I hung up the phone I was left with all sorts of questions and I knew that many of the physicians (if not all) including the brainwashed nurses, were all complicit  in these crimes against humanity. They are blinded  and in some cases  willfully ignorant in following orders and guidelines that are killing people and making them more depressed and suicidal.  This is a money racket and deadly western allopathic medical model that is killing many people every day by pathological liars and doctors who have been formatted into thinking all the same way in medical school from day 1.  Just like the military soldiers go through.  Total brainwash and no respect to their ‘oath’.  No empathy, no understanding for their patients, just treating them in numbers so they can have money to pay their wives and houses and retire.  That’s it, that’s all!  This is not the future of medicine that we all deserve.  This is medical tyranny.  This is a medical model to make people sick and kill them.  Shame on the Canadian Medical Association and all the quacks that are part of their organizations.

September 17, 2020, Austin, Texas

On October 3, 2020 from 9am - 6pm, a nonpartisan group of patriots and freedom seekers will gather at the Texas State Capitol in Austin for an educational summit and peaceful protest to take a stand for our Constitutional rights amid rising government overreach.  There will be experts on various topics including: COVID-19, health and religious freedoms, business rights, gun rights, public education, censorship and law.
The constitution of the United States of America secures and affirms our God-Given rights. Today's social climate in the USA has infringed, violated and challenged these rights almost unimpeded. column31: HOW ACCURATE IS THE COVID-19 DATA THAT GUIDES LOCKDOWN MEASURES? With a purported second wave now under way, lockdown measures have again intensified across Canada. The data used to drive the emergency health policies, however, do not stand on solid, credible ground. Deaths, for the first time in history, are not being attributed to an actual cause of death but an accompanying infection, as is the case with Covid-19. This new guideline was recommended by the World Health Organization (WHO), but the public was never given an explanation for this change in coding deaths by the WHO or its governments. On June 23, 2020, Ontario Minister of Health Christine Elliott confirmed that "there are situations where there are other pre-existing conditions that may actually be the cause of the loss, rather than Covid. Covid is there but may not have been the cause of death." (1) Curiously, Canadian media outlets have not reported or questioned this epidemiologically significant change in the way that deaths are recorded. The reporting of daily new cases has been the one metric that has remained since the start of the WHO-called Covid-19 pandemic. The initial projection of deaths, the metric by which many countries instituted lockdown measures, quickly fell from government and media narrative, as those numbers were grossly exaggerated worldwide. In Canada, 226,000 to 526,000 deaths (est. 2% fatality) were initially projected under strong measures. Since then, PCR tests have been the global tool that governments have used to drive emergency policies and measures. The accuracy of reporting positive Covid-19 cases has recently come under scrutiny, however, especially since a New York Times review of positive cases in three states revealed that as many as 90% of cases had "barely any virus" and were likely not infectious. (3) The reason: PCR tests were set at levels that magnified the amount of virus 100x - 1000x the actual amount in the body. Earlier on July 30, 2020, Ontario’s associate chief medical officer of health, Dr. Barbara Yaffe validated this finding by the New York Times review, “If you’re testing in a population that doesn’t have very much Covid, you’ll get false positives almost half the time. That is, the person doesn’t actually have Covid.” With such inaccuracies in the reporting of new cases during a purported second wave of Covid-19, should the government abandon this metric to gauge the severity of Covid-19 and its potential impact on Canadians and instead use the number of hospitalizations and deaths--numbers less subject to gross inaccuracies--to guide our health measures? With the health and financial destinies of millions of Canadians resting in the hands of accurate and transparent government data and policies, it's a move that makes medical and political sense. (1) https://www.680news.com/2020/06/23/toronto-child-under-9-dies-with-covid-19-but-not-as-a-result-of-the-virus/ (2) https://www.ctvnews.ca/health/coronavirus/pm-trudeau-this-will-be-the-new-normal-until-a-vaccine-is-developed-1.4889651 (3) https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/29/health/coronavirus-testing.html ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ QUELLE EST LA PRÉCISION DES DONNÉES COVID-19 QUI GUIDENT LES MESURES SANITAIRES? Alors que la prétendue deuxième vague est en cours, les mesures sanitaires se sont de nouveau intensifiées partout au Canada. Cependant, les données utilisées pour conduire les politiques sanitaires d'urgence ne reposent pas sur des bases solides et crédibles. Les décès, pour la première fois dans l'histoire, ne sont pas attribués à une cause réelle de décès mais à une infection qui l'accompagne, comme c'est le cas avec Covid-19. Cette nouvelle directive a été recommandée par l'Organisation mondiale de la santé (OMS), mais le public n'a jamais reçu d'explication pour ce changement de codage des décès par l'OMS ou ses gouvernements. Le 23 juin 2020, la ministre de la Santé de l'Ontario, Christine Elliott, a confirmé qu '"il y a des situations où il existe d'autres conditions préexistantes qui pourraient en fait être la cause de la perte, plutôt que Covid. Covid est là mais peut-être pas en avoir été la cause de la mort." (1) Curieusement, les médias canadiens n'ont pas rapporté ni remis en question ce changement épidémiologiquement significatif dans la façon dont les décès sont enregistrés. La publication des nouveaux cas quotidiens est la seule mesure qui est restée depuis le début de la pandémie du Covid-19, telle que nommée par l'OMS. column36:
Well, here goes ROUND 2!!! People said our first boat parade was their favorite day on the St Johns to date! This is a family friendly event! My kids haven’t stopped talking about the last one. 😃 Bring the kids! Let’s show our support loud and proud for our great POTUS and keep Seminole County RED! 🇺🇸 Last time we had a few surprise flyovers by seaplane and then again by prop plane, drone coverage and a headcount of about 1,000 between boaters and spectators on land!!!

No boat? NO PROBLEM! Read on!

———————————————————-

Starting point @ Mullet Lake. 

Head north through Lake Monroe - hug the West side of the lake/channel for spectators. 

Ending point will be anywhere between Redneck Beach and Highbanks Marina. You may also choose to congregate and anchor in Lake Monroe where road traffic, trail walkers and local fishers will be able to spectate.

Rentals booked out QUICK last time! Don’t miss your opportunity to snag a boat because you put it off! Book now if you’re going to need one!

———————————————————-

*** NON-BOATER SPECTATING INFO ***

1. Gators Riverside Grill

5. Lake Monroe Wayside Park — FISHING PIER. (Land Captain: @Kali Vermillion)
6. 1792 bridge over St Johns River. Parking @ Lake Monroe Park, DeBary (Land Captain: @Kathleen Kratt)

With only scientific and epidemiological data and unwavering integrity with respect to the duty of any government official holding office, he has stood alone in the Ontario parliament fighting to have the government be open, transparent and accountable to the evidence and not political objectives. 

As many Ontarians--and Canadians--have struggled with their livelihood, access to healthcare and equitable rights in having mask exemptions honoured, many have been hearing his message and seeing the truth behind the veil of the Ontario government's actions.

As positive cases, of which Doug Ford recently admitted that 70-80% have no symptoms, are being diagnosed with an unreliable PCR test that detects up to 50% false positives, cases have predictably risen to record levels with the opening of test facilities in pharmacies. This spike has not fortunately, however, come with the more important metrics of increased hospitalizations and deaths. 

It must, therefore, be asked, when will the government be transparent and react with policies that reflect the mild nature of the Covid-19 virus?

MISREPRESENTATION BY THE VICTORIAN DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH ON COVID REPORT AT LEO’S HARTWELL

Open letter to our customers,

THE FACTS IN BRIEF:

1. A customer diagnosed with covid19 entered Leo’s Hartwell on Saturday September 26, between the hours on 2:00 & 2:20PM.
2. Leo’s Hartwell wasn’t advised by the Victorian Department of Health until Thursday, October 1 at 3:45PM – 5 days after the fact.
3. The Department of Health advised that a ‘deep clean’ was not necessary and advised only to clean touch surfaces. The Department of Health advised that team members should only be checked if they display symptoms.
4. Leo’s deemed a ‘deep clean’ essential and executes this with external contractors on morning of Friday October 2 at 5am. Staff were advised and monitored, with several checked for covid19, with no cases reported.
5. This case was deemed as ‘low risk’ by the Department of Health due to customer and cashier interaction for less than 15 minutes.
6. The Department of Health refused to inform us as to which cashier interacted with the infected customer, due to privacy laws.
7. On the morning of Friday October 2, we again tried to find out the cashier who served the customer, in order to protect our team member and the potential for further infection, without success.
8. In a back flip, the Department of Health reported Leo’s as a ‘high risk location,’ which naturally created media interest.
9. The Department of Health further erroneously indicated two separate incidents at Leo’s Hartwell, later retracting its second statement as an error.
10. Out of concern for customers and staff safety, on the morning of Wednesday 7 October, Leo’s Hartwell initiated a further deep clean. This was carried out by ‘Bio Safety’ executing a full hospital grade disinfection using thermal fogging, and a certificate of compliance was issued.

FURTHER FACTS:

1. The only store implicated was Leo’s Hartwell, not Kew, nor Heidelberg locations.
2. We have not had one case amongst staff at Leo’s Fine Food & Wine of Covid19. 
3. Since the infected person entered the store at Hartwell, there has not been a single transmission of Covid19 among our staff or other customers.
4. We continue to uphold high standards with implementation of our covid19 safe program.

As a valued customer, please be rest assured that we have taken every precaution over and above the recommendations of the Department of Health to ensure your safety in our stores.

Please feel free to share this document; as it is important for people to know the facts of this misrepresentation by the Department of Health.

We thank you for your continued support.

Kind Regards,

The team at Leo’s Fine Food & Wine.

column31: Free exercise of religion is a fundamental constitutionally protected freedom. A blanket shutdown of synagogues is a violation of the United States Constitution and the Religious Freedom Restoration Act of 1993. H.R.1308 - Religious Freedom Restoration Act of 1993 "Religious Freedom Restoration Act of 1993 - Prohibits any agency, department, or official of the United States or any State (the government) from substantially burdening a person's exercise of religion even if the burden results from a rule of general applicability, except that the government may burden a person's exercise of religion only if it demonstrates that application of the burden to the person: (1) furthers a compelling governmental interest; and (2) is the least restrictive means of furthering that compelling governmental interest." For over an hour, rally participants demonstrated their enthusiastic support for Newport Beach law enforcement personnel. This announcement is to advise you the next Back the Blue rally will be this coming Sunday in Costa Mesa. We hope you can attend and bring the family and friends along to demonstrate your support for the police and law enforcement throughout our community. Please see details below for the SUNDAY October 18th, 2020 rally.** **You’re invited to an ACT for America** **“BACK THE BLUE” Rally** **To honor/support local law enforcement** **SUNDAY, October 18, 2020** **1:00 to 2:00 PM** ***WHERE RALLY WILL START AND END:* **The rally will officially start at **1:00pm**, at the *intersection* of **FAIR Dr** and **VANGUARD WAY** in Costa Mesa. The Costa Mesa Police Department building is located on the corner of that intersection (99 Fair Dr.). You are welcome to invite your friends and family to the rally. We will rally for 5-10 minutes, on the *public sidewalk,* in front of the Police Department. This rally provides an opportunity for us to demonstrate and express our appreciation for law enforcement personnel locally and across the country. We will then reposition the rally by walking down Fair Dr. (approx. 1/2 mile) toward **Newport Blvd**, and stand/rally on the *public sidewalk* intersection at Fair Dr and Newport Blvd for 40-45 minutes to show our support for local law enforcement. At the conclusion of our rally, individuals shall return to the City Hall parking lot and return any loaned rally materials before departing for the day. ***PRE-RALLY GATHERING:* At 12:40pm-12:55pm **meet in the *public parking lot adjacent the **Costa Mesa City Hall** (**77 Fair Drive**)*. There will be an informal gathering to receive rally instructions & *loaner*signs or flags if you don’t bring your own demonstration materials.** **Wear patriotic color clothing, if available. No bull horns, air horns or noise making devices allowed. Bring US flags and home-made signs showing support for law enforcement. ***FOR PLANNING PURPOSES PLEASE SIGN-UP:*** If you plan on participating in this event, please sign-up by 10:00am Sunday October 18th, to Bob Gast (949-228-7206) or Kash Ronvelia (714-874-5171). Phone call or text is fine. Note: There will be free bottled water available before the start of the event. There are over 70 signs, printed 2-sides, in various sizes and a small quantity of US flags that can be loaned to you for use during the event. ***These items must be returned at the end of the event***. Newsom’s directive. * Standing and/or walking on the public sidewalk is up to rally participant’s preference. * Always hold signs, banner and/or flag in safe and non-threating manner. * Be courteous & respectful to all rally participants and those observing the rally. * Use common sense & *controlled* ***reserved*** response if harassed or threatened by another person. * Remember the rally is for you to peacefully demonstrating your support of law enforcement; have fun & be safe in the process. * If at any time you feel unsafe, immediately leave the rally & move to a safe location. * Return all “loaned” rally materials (flags/signs) at the end of the rally. **Don’ts:** * It is unlawful to be on a roadway, unless you are crossing in a traffic light controlled crosswalk…DO **NOT** STEP onto the roadway at any time during the rally. * On Fair Dr & Newport Blvd do **NOT** hinder/block vehicles from entering or exiting the roadway. * Don’t respond verbally or non-verbally to anyone expressing/displaying their opposition to the rally or individuals therein. * Don’t confront/argue with anyone expressing a negative attitude or position regarding law enforcement or our 1st Amendment rights of free speech and assembly. column34: M 0 ALL ALL The Telegraph LOCKDOWNS LOCKDOWN URE MUST NOT TELEGRAPH.CO.UK Herd immunity could have saved more lives than lockdown, study suggests
column36:
HERD IMMUNITY COULD HAVE SAVED MORE LIVES THAN LOCKDOWNS: EDINBURGH UNIVERSITY STUDY

"Blanket social distancing and the closure of schools may have cost more lives than if herd immunity had been allowed to build slowly in the community, a University of Edinburgh study found.

A reanalysis of the Imperial College modelling that led to lockdown in March shows that shutting schools and preventing youngsters from mingling may have had the counterintuitive effect of actually killing more people.

In a study published in the British Medical Journal, Edinburgh University predicted that over the entire course of the pandemic, keeping children out of classrooms would increase deaths by between 80,000 and 95,000. Likewise, social distancing of everyone, rather than just the over-70s, could cost between 149,000 and 178,000 lives. Experts say the virus was able to spread faster to vulnerable people once lockdown measures were introduced than if some level of immunity had been allowed to build up in the young. 

It comes as thousands of scientists across the world signed the Great Barrington Declaration, calling for an end to lockdown for young and healthy people.

The Government locked down the country after Imperial modelling showed that 500,000 people could die and the NHS would be overwhelmed. But Imperial had also predicted that no mitigation strategy could lower deaths to fewer than 200,000 without a vaccine, and suppressing the virus would merely delay an even deadlier resurgence.

The authors of the new paper, who rediscovered the figures in their reappraisal, said the Government appeared to have chosen to protect the NHS in the short term, rather than save lives throughout the whole epidemic. Although it reduced peak demand for ICU beds, it prolonged the epidemic, resulting in more Covid-19 deaths in long-term.

Lead author Graeme Ackland, Professor of computer simulation at the University of Edinburgh, said: 'In March the Government had to make a decision: did they want to save lives or beds? Lockdown does mean that the number of deaths goes down, so there is a short-term gain, but it leads to long-term pain. If you had done nothing, it would all be over by now. It wouldn’t even have been completely lunatic to do nothing.'

The study also found that shutting schools ‘leads to more overall deaths from Covid-19’ than allowing them to remain open. 'This is because it prevents herd immunity building up among the healthy and young, who face only a tiny risk of dying from the disease. The virus would bounce back as soon as measures involving school closures are lifted, infecting more vulnerable populations and resulting in ‘more deaths, but later’. Figures showing the dangers of closing schools and blanket social distancing were reported in the original Imperial paper, but many experts did not notice them, it is claimed. 'I talked to people on SPI-M and Sage and they hadn’t seen them,' added Professoor Ackland.

‘Lockdowns essentially just postpone these deaths and prevent immunity building up... in some cases resulting in more deaths long-term. The way out of any epidemic is herd immunity, which is when enough people in the population are infected that the virus can’t spread. We need to focus on protecting older people who are going to be affected by coronavirus, not people who are not,' stated Professor Ackland."

Can you tell the difference between these kids?

By requiring kids to wear masks - whether it’s in stores, in schools, or a public place - you are robbing them of their ONE hope of being found in the event that they get taken - their faces. 

Did you know that more than 2,000 missing-child reports are filed EVERY DAY and that many of them can be easily found when parents provide specific details about their physical appearance and a photo of THEIR FACE? 

Did you KNOW that a child in AMERICA is over 66,000 x more likely to be human trafficked than to die from COVID-19? 

So DO YOU REALIZE that by requiring children over the age of 2 to wear a mask, you are making child abduction & human trafficking SO MUCH EASIER on the offenders? 

Don’t believe me? 

Elizabeth Smart was abducted for 9 months and her abductor took her out in public ALL THE TIME. Her face was plastered EVERYWHERE and burned into everyone’s minds. Everyone was looking for her. 

She was even questioned by the police prior to being rescued - but because he made her wear a mask, nobody could tell it was her. 

Put a hat and a mask on child, and they look no different than the 2000 other kids around them.

This issue is not about politics or school or the virus. This is about the CHILDREN.

Making a child wear a mask will protect them from a virus that they may or may not get anyways, that they may or may not have already had, and it will also open the door for so many offenders who have lurked in the shadows afraid to ACT to do just that: 

Go out and actually take a child.

column34: !Landmark Ruling! Governor's COVID Orders Violate Constitutional Authority.
column36:
In a landmark ruling with far-reaching implications, the Michigan Supreme Court decided Friday that Gov. Gretchen Whitmer violated her constitutional authority by continuing to issue orders to combat COVID-19 without the approval of state lawmakers.

The order essentially brings an end to Whitmer's ability to use emergency powers without legislative approval.

“All public officials must respect the right of the people to govern themselves at all times, especially during a crisis.” 

“The United States Constitution guarantees a republican form of government to every state in our free country. The Constitution does not permit any public official unlawfully to restrict our liberty,” Assistant Attorney General Eric Dreiband of the Civil Rights Division said in a statement.

"The governor had no right to extend the state of emergency over the Legislature’s objection. Our constitution matters, and this was a big win for our democratic process," Chatfield said.

Michigan Republican Party Chairwoman Laura Cox said the ruling marked "a great day for the people of Michigan."

"Gov. Whitmer overexerted her powers," Cox said. "The Legislature wants to be a willing partner in dealing with COVID-19, and Governor Whitmer should recognize their duly delegated role.”

The ruling concluded the 1945 act violated the Michigan Constitution because it delegated to the executive branch the legislative powers of state government and allowed the executive branch to exercise those powers indefinitely.

The state's high court ruled 4-3 that a state law allowing the governor to declare emergencies and keep them in place without legislative input is unconstitutional. 

The court was unanimous in ruling that a separate law — the 1976 Emergency Management Act  — did not give Whitmer the power, after April 30, to issue or renew any executive orders related to the COVID-19 pandemic after 28 days without Legislative approval.

"Anybody that is in the courts right now will point to this ruling and should win," said Wright, referencing other pending lawsuits against Whitmer. 

We need More Freedom and Less Government.
